    "body": "This issue is reproduced by `cd` to a directory symlinked to another directory under git management when `directory.repo_root_style` is set.\n\n```toml\n[directory]\nrepo_root_style = 'blue'\n```\n\n```sh\nmkdir -p /tmp/foo/bar\ncd /tmp/foo && git init\nln -s /tmp/foo/bar /tmp/baz\ncd /tmp/baz\n```\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
